        {
            "title": "達美樂執行長預測業績疲軟後全行業將面臨困境",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0D2SHkyLsCiVGgDP9LnnZw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED280E4_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"達美樂\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:達美樂;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/達美樂\">達美樂</a>披薩(Domino’s Pizza)股價週一盤中下跌10%,此前該公司公布的美國同店銷售增長低於預期,並下調全年預測。執行長羅素·韋納(Russell Weiner)警告稱,其他速食連鎖店可能也會報告類似的困境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家披薩連鎖店的國內同店銷售額僅增長0.9%,低於華爾街分析師基於StreetAccount估計預期的2.3%增長。達美樂還將全年美國同店銷售預測下調至低個位數增長,低於此前預計的3%增長。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b6eeb337-e0bb-342c-a470-0c5f2860b65c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韋納週一向CNBC表示,他預計更多速食連鎖店將報告來自冬季天氣和疲軟消費者信心的不利因素,由於美國與以色列對伊朗戰爭導致燃油價格上漲,消費者信心在3月份有所下降。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「率先發布業績的壞處之一是你無法聽到其他人的情況,」韋納表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">達美樂還面臨來自競爭對手披薩連鎖店棒約翰(<span><span>Papa John’s</span></span>)和必勝客(Pizza Hut)日益激烈的競爭。韋納表示,競爭對手正透過新的促銷活動來應對達美樂的市場份額增長,儘管他仍預計棒約翰和必勝客將報告本季同店銷售下降。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「達美樂的廣告預算比我們第二和第三大競爭對手的總和還要多,」韋納說。「而且這些競爭對手都在待售,所以我們知道他們現在的情況並不好。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">達美樂股價在過去一年中已損失近三分之一的價值,該公司市值降至約112億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">星巴克(Starbucks)計劃於週二收盤後公布業績,而墨西哥捲餅連鎖店Chipotle Mexican Grill和必勝客母公司百勝餐飲集團(Yum Brands,百勝還擁有肯德基和塔可鐘)預計將於週三公布業績。棒約翰將於下週四公布業績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
